    {
      "para_id": "Q001484.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) For Nanše , the mighty lady , the lady of the boundaries , his lady , Gudea , ruler of Lagaš , made an eternal thing appear : he built and restored her E-sirara , the mountain rising from among the houses , in her beloved city , Niĝin , ( and ) restored her lofty city wall ."
    }
  ],
